quran[4{c,v,t}:
2,253,"yeh rasool ( jo hamari taraf se insanon ki hadaayat par mamoor hue ) hum ne un ko aik dosray se barh charh kar martabay ataa kiye un mein koi aisa tha jis se khuda khud hum kalaam howa, kisi ko is ne doosri hisiton se buland darjay diye, aur aakhir mein ( hazrat ) Eesa Ibn maryam(alh-e-salam) ko roshan nishanain ataa kee aur rooh pak se is ki madad ki agar Allah chahta, to mumkin nah tha ke inn rasloon Rasolo-n ke baad jo log roshan nishanain dekh chuke thay, woh aapas mein lartay magar ( Allah ki Mushiyat yeh nah thi ke woh logon ko jabran ikhtilaaf se rokay, is wajah se ) unhon ne baahum ikhtilaaf kya, phir koi imaan laya aur kisi ne kufar ki raah ikhtiyar ki haan, Allah chahta, to woh hargiz nah lartay, magar Allah jo chahta hai karta hai"
2,254,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jo kuch maal mata hum ne tum ko bakhsha hai, is mein se kharch karo, qabal is ke ke woh din aeye, jis mein nah kharedo farokht hogi, nah dosti kaam aeye gi aur nah sifarish chalay gi aur zalim asal mein wohi hain, jo kufar ki rawish ikhtiyar karte hain"
2,255,"Allah , woh zindah Javed hasti, jo tamam kaayenaat ko sambhale hue hai, uss ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai woh nah sota hai aur nah ussay ongh lagti hai zameen aur asmano mein jo kuch hai, usi ka hai kon hai jo uss ki janab mein uss ki ijazat ke baghair sifarish kar sakay? jo kuch bundon ke samnay hai usay bhi woh jaanta hai aur jo kuch unn se oojhal hai, is se bhi woh waaqif hai aur uss ki maloomat mein se koi cheez unn ki girift idraak mein nahi askati ila yeh ke kisi cheez ka ilm woh khud hi unn ko dena chahay uss ki hukoomat asmano aur zameen par chhai hui hai aur unn ki nigehbani is ke liye koi thaka dainay wala kaam nahi hai bas wohi aik buzurag o bartar zaat hai"
2,256,"deen ke muamlay mein koi zor zabardasti nahi hai sahih baat ghalat khayalat se a lag chhant kar rakh di gayi hai ab jo koi Taghoot ka inkaar kar ke Allah par imaan le aaya, uss ne aik aisa mazboot sahara thaam liya, jo kabhi totnay wala nahi, aur Allah ( jis ka sahara is ne liya hai ) sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai"
